text: Nevenka Pogačnik (born 14 April 1936) is a Slovenian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
